<div class="mdui-typo"><h1 id="dictation-n">dictation <strong><em>n</em></strong></h1>
<p>英 /dɪk'teɪʃn/    美 /dɪk'teɪʃn/  </p>
<h2 id="_1">释义</h2>
<h4 id="1u">1.<strong>[U] 口述；口授：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>I wrote the letter at his dictation. 
我照他的口述写了这封信。</p></div>

<h4 id="2-c-u">2.★ <strong>[C] &amp; [U] 听写；听写材料：</strong></h4>
<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>We <strong>did a dictation</strong> today. 
我们今天听写了。</p></div>

<div class="mdui-typo"><blockquote><p>Hand in your dictations, please. 
请把你们的听写交上来。</p></div>

<h2 id="_2">真题解析</h2>
<ol>
<li>The English teacher gives the class a <strong><em>_</em></strong>_ (听写) almost every day.   （2008 全国）  </li>
</ol>
<p>答案：
1. dictation  </p></div>